                                            <td class="description">      Hi team,<br/>
<br/>
please validate this mission:<br/>
<br/>
[https://ucr.cfapps.eu10-004.hana.ondemand.com/#/UseCase/view/UC00003969]<br/>
<br/>
I have already reached out to the mission owner regarding system access and will add the info if required later on.<br/>
<br/>
Thank you very much!<br/>
<br/>
Update: SFSF System access:<br/>
<br/>
 <br/>
|*name*|*value*|<br/>
|companyID|SFPART066608|<br/>
|bot username|botapi|<br/>
|bot password|YBfbx67tcqiTs*!EY|<br/>
|offer type|Online Offer|<br/>
|botstep|Ready to Send|<br/>
|sfURL|[https://pmsalesdemo8.successfactors.com|https://pmsalesdemo8.successfactors.com/]|<br/>
|logEmail| you own email|<br/>
|outputLog| local folder where output excel will be created|<br/>
<br/>
 <br/>
 # login to that SFSF instance with the bot user.<br/>
 # Go to recruiting, scroll down in the job requisitions and click on the candidates of the requisition 3076<br/>
 # There are some candidates in the status Offer-&gt; Offer sent<br/>
 # Move them to the status Offer-&gt;Ready to send <br/>
<br/>
The bot will look for candidates in &quot;Ready to send&quot;, extend the offer, and move them to &quot;Offer sent”<br/>
<br/>
IMPORTANT: I have done some updates on the automation, get the most up to date here:<br/>
<br/>
[Offer Letter Distribution - January 2026.mtar|https://sap-my.sharepoint.com/:u:/p/pedro_iranzo_egea/IQCPsGZ7CXlyQpTzIEYUHiqtAVX0YfwYLK8F90JC8HtZ2c4?email=manish.kumar40%40sap.com&amp;e=g14GYv]
